snippet.title: Michael Anderson - HL2: The Masked Prisoner
snippet.description:
http://www.mikeadesign.com
"The Masked Prisoner" explores the untold stories of several Half Life characters - taking place in a prison on the outskirts of City 17.

Art fidelity for this project is only 1st pass/rough blockout quality.
